{
  "number": 84,
  "name": {
    "ar": "الانشقاق",
    "en": "Al-Inshiqaq"
  },
  "verses_count": 25,
  "verses": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": {
        "ar": "إِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنشَقَّتۡ",
        "en": "When the sky has split [open]"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ",
        "en": "And has responded to its Lord and was obligated [to do so]"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَإِذَا ٱلۡأَرۡضُ مُدَّتۡ",
        "en": "And when the earth has been extended"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَأَلۡقَتۡ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتۡ",
        "en": "And has cast out that within it and relinquished [it]"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَأَذِنَتۡ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتۡ",
        "en": "And has responded to its Lord and was obligated [to do so]"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": {
        "ar": "يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدۡحٗا فَمُلَٰقِيهِ",
        "en": "O mankind, indeed you are laboring toward your Lord with [great] exertion and will meet it"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": {
        "ar": "فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ",
        "en": "Then as for he who is given his record in his right hand"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": {
        "ar": "فَسَوۡفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابٗا يَسِيرٗا",
        "en": "He will be judged with an easy account"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورٗا",
        "en": "And return to his people in happiness"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهۡرِهِۦ",
        "en": "But as for he who is given his record behind his back"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": {
        "ar": "فَسَوۡفَ يَدۡعُواْ ثُبُورٗا",
        "en": "He will cry out for destruction"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَيَصۡلَىٰ سَعِيرًا",
        "en": "And [enter to] burn in a Blaze"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": {
        "ar": "إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِيٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ مَسۡرُورًا",
        "en": "Indeed, he had [once] been among his people in happiness"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": {
        "ar": "إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ",
        "en": "Indeed, he had thought he would never return [to Allah]"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": {
        "ar": "بَلَىٰٓۚ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرٗا",
        "en": "But yes! Indeed, his Lord was ever of him, Seeing"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": {
        "ar": "فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ",
        "en": "So I swear by the twilight glow"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَٱلَّيۡلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ",
        "en": "And [by] the night and what it envelops"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا ٱتَّسَقَ",
        "en": "And [by] the moon when it becomes full"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": {
        "ar": "لَتَرۡكَبُنَّ طَبَقًا عَن طَبَقٖ",
        "en": "[That] you will surely experience state after state"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": {
        "ar": "فَمَا لَهُمۡ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ",
        "en": "So what is [the matter] with them [that] they do not believe"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَإِذَا قُرِئَ عَلَيۡهِمُ ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ لَا يَسۡجُدُونَۤ۩",
        "en": "And when the Qur'an is recited to them, they do not prostrate [to Allah]"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": {
        "id": 14,
        "recommended": true,
        "obligatory": false
      }
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": {
        "ar": "بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ يُكَذِّبُونَ",
        "en": "But those who have disbelieved deny"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": {
        "ar": "وَٱللَّهُ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَا يُوعُونَ",
        "en": "And Allah is most knowing of what they keep within themselves"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": {
        "ar": "فَبَشِّرۡهُم بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ",
        "en": "So give them tidings of a painful punishment"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": {
        "ar": "إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّـٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ أَجۡرٌ غَيۡرُ مَمۡنُونِۭ",
        "en": "Except for those who believe and do righteous deeds. For them is a reward uninterrupted"
      },
      "juz": 30,
      "page": 589,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ],
  "revelation_place": "مكية"
}